{"tid":545403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那去年保險業淨營運現金流下跌65%","createTime":"2018-01-30T13:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T13:03:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01655935766a22246d93dfc2fcbe7dd2ec6bec0d","tid":545403,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1378186-20180130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1378186-20180130.htm&d=Ki1wKPhT73NM2HnZ6osEsDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8316696e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1378186-20180130.htm&h=6fb36bf2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1378186-20180130.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外電引述消息人士報道，支那保險業去年淨營運現金流下跌65%，跌至6330億元支那幣。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士引述政府備忘錄中的數據表示，壽險業者淨營業現金流下跌47%，產險及意外險就轉為負數。"}]}